      "content": "sometimes \"taking a break\" doesn't feel like enough. like, what if the break is meant to be permanent? it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen because staying like this is just unbearable. i look at him and then i look at myself and i just don't see a reason to stay in this world without him. it feels like i'm just staying for no reason at all.",
